 \"to\": 2023}, {\"ngram\": \"an Asian Games gold\", \"from\": 2028, \"to\": 2047}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She was also crowned Asian champion in 2021.\", \"from\": 2049, \"to\": 2093, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2070, \"end\": 2075, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999999799911, \"rank\": 1.995368947975141e-11, \"text\": \"Asian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Games\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She was on the cusp of making history as her country's first wrestler to win an Olympic silver, and possibly gold, when fate intervened.\", \"from\": 2095, \"to\": 2231, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the cusp\", \"from\": 2106, \"to\": 2114}, {\"ngram\": \"history\", \"from\": 2125, \"to\": 2132}, {\"ngram\": \"her country's first wrestler\", \"from\": 2136, \"to\": 2164}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic silver\", \"from\": 2172, \"to\": 2189}, {\"ngram\": \"possibly gold\", \"from\": 2195, \"to\": 2208}, {\"ngram\": \"fate\", \"from\": 2215, \"to\": 2219}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When she was weighed on the morning of her final match on Tuesday, she came in about 100g overweight and was instantly disqualified.\", \"from\": 2232, \"to\": 2364, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the morning\", \"from\": 2256, \"to\": 2267}, {\"ngram\": \"her final match\", \"from\": 2271, \"to\": 2286}, {\"ngram\": \"Tuesday\", \"from\": 2290, \"to\": 2297}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It is with regret that the Indian contingent shares news of the disqualification of Vinesh Phogat from women's wrestling 50kg class,\\\" the Indian Olympic Association said.\", \"from\": 2366, \"to\": 2537, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2394, \"end\": 2400, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_people\", \"score\": 0.9999998905655108, \"rank\": 1.0903925668190851e-07, \"text\": \"Indian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org