Sakshi Malik, she demonstrated on the streets of the capital Delhi to demand action against Mr Singh over sexual assault and intimidation charges, only to be manhandled by police.\", \"from\": 2993, \"to\": 3218, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3039, \"end\": 3051, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sakshi_Malik\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.094353708424377e-39, \"text\": \"Sakshi Malik\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sakshi_Malik\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sakshi_Malik\"}, {\"begin\": 3100, \"end\": 3105, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Delhi\", \"score\": 0.9996422021364677, \"rank\": 0.00035792592850948885, \"text\": \"Delhi\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Delhi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Delhi\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fellow Olympians\", \"from\": 3004, \"to\": 3020}, {\"ngram\": \"Bajrang Punia\", \"from\": 3021, \"to\": 3034}, {\"ngram\": \"the streets\", \"from\": 3073, \"to\": 3084}, {\"ngram\": \"the capital\", \"from\": 3088, \"to\": 3099}, {\"ngram\": \"action\", \"from\": 3116, \"to\": 3122}, {\"ngram\": \"Mr Singh\", \"from\": 3131, \"to\": 3139}, {\"ngram\": \"sexual assault and intimidation charges\", \"from\": 3145, \"to\": 3184}, {\"ngram\": \"police\", \"from\": 3211, \"to\": 3217}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They called off the protest after then federal sports minister Anurag Thakur promised a fair investigation but resumed it when Mr Singh was re-elected the federation's chief.\", \"from\": 3220, \"to\": 3394, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3283, \"end\": 3296, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anurag_Thakur\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Anurag Thakur\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anurag_Thakur\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anurag_Thakur\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the protest\", \"from\": 3236, \"to\": 3247}, {\"ngram\": \"a fair investigation\", \"from\": 3306, \"to\": 3326}, {\"ngram\": \"Mr Singh\", \"from\": 3347, \"to\": 3355}, {\"ngram\": \"the federation's chief\", \"from\": 3371, \"to\": 3393}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The wrestlers were assaulted and detained by police when they marched to the new parliament on the day of its inauguration last May.\", \"from\": 3396, \"to\": 3528, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The wrestlers\", \"from\": 3396, \"to\": 3409}, {\"ngram\": \"police\", \"from\": 3441, \"to\": 3447}, {\"ngram\": \"the new parliament\", \"from\": 3469, \"to\": 3487}, {\"ngram\": \"the day\", \"from\": 3491, \"to\": 3498}, {\"ngram\": \"its inauguration\", \"from\": 3502, \"to\": 3518}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the peak of protest, with her career on the line, Vinesh was asked about the source of her courage.\", \"from\": 3530, \"to\": 3632, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3583, \"end\": 3589, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Vinesh\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the peak\", \"from\": 3533, \"to\": 3541}, {\"ngram\": \"protest\", \"from\": 3545, \"to\": 3552}, {\"ngram\": \"her career\", \"from\": 3559, \"to\": 3569}, {\"ngram\": \"the line\", \"from\": 3573, \"to\": 3581}, {\"ngram\": \"the source\", \"from\": 3606, \"to\": 3616}, {\"ngram\": \"her courage\", \"from\": 3620, \"to\": 3631}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's from my mother,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 3633, \"to\": 3665, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my mother\", \"from\": 3644, \"to\": 3653}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She recounted her mother's struggle as a single parent and battle with cancer.\", \"from\": 3667, \"to\": 3745, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her mother's struggle\", \"from\": 3681, \"to\": 3702}, {\"ngram\": \"a single parent\", \"from\": 3706, \"to\": 3721}, {\"ngram\": \"battle\", \"from\": 3726, \"to\": 3732}, {\"ngram\": \"cancer\", \"from\": 3738, \"to\": 3744}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She was about 32 when she became a widow,\\\" Vinesh toldThe Indian Express.\", \"from\": 3745, \"to\": 3819, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a widow\", \"from\": 3779, \"to\": 3786}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I feel sad thinking about it.\", \"from\": 3821, \"to\": 3851, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She struggled for us.\", \"from\": 3852, \"to\": 3873, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 3870, \"to\": 3872}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In that struggle we did not even realise when we grew up.\", \"from\": 3874, \"to\": 3931, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that struggle\", \"from\": 3877, \"to\": 3890}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A single woman, she would be taunted by others, how they treated her.\", \"from\": 3932, \"to\": 4001, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A single woman\", \"from\": 3932, \"to\": 3946}, {\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 3972, \"to\": 3978}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She did not even know where to sit, where to get off.\", \"from\": 4003, \"to\": 4057, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"No one supported her.\", \"from\": 4058, \"to\": 4079, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"No one\", \"from\": 4058, \"to\": 4064}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We grew up seeing her struggle.\", \"from\": 4080, \"to\": 4111, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her struggle\", \"from\": 4098, \"to\": 4110}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If a single woman like that, illiterate, could fight the society on her own and make us big wrestlers, then we can do it too.\", \"from\": 4112, \"to\": 4237, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a single woman\", \"from\": 4115, \"to\": 4129}, {\"ngram\": \"the society\", \"from\": 4165, \"to\": 4176}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 4197, \"to\": 4199}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If we do not speak out today then all the struggles of my mother would have gone to waste.\", \"from\": 4239, \"to\": 4330, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all the struggles\", \"from\": 4274, \"to\": 4291}, {\"ngram\": \"my mother\", \"from\": 4295, \"to\": 4304}, {\"ngram\": \"waste\", \"from\": 4324, \"to\": 4329}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I won medals, that's all right, but if we win this battle, she will proudly say, 'I gave birth to them'.\", \"from\": 4331, \"to\": 4435, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"medals\", \"from\": 4337, \"to\": 4343}, {\"ngram\": \"this battle\", \"from\": 4377, \"to\": 4388}, {\"ngram\": \"birth\", \"from\": 4420, \"to\": 4425}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am proud that my mother showed so much strength and character, I guess that's in me as well.\", \"from\": 4436, \"to\": 4530, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my mother\", \"from\": 4452, \"to\": 4461}, {\"ngram\": \"so much strength\", \"from\": 4469, \"to\": 4485}, {\"ngram\": \"character\", \"from\": 4490, \"to\": 4499}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Even my father was like that.\", \"from\": 4531, \"to\": 4560, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Even my father\", \"from\": 4531, \"to\": 4545}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am also like that.\\\"\", \"from\": 4561, \"to\": 4582, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In a public voice call on Tuesday, she told her smiling mother that she would win gold.\", \"from\": 4584, \"to\": 4671, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a public voice call\", \"from\": 4587, \"to\": 4606}, {\"ngram\": \"Tuesday\", \"from\": 4610, \"to\": 4617}, {\"ngram\": \"her smiling mother\", \"from\": 4628, \"to\": 4646}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 4666, \"to\": 4670}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Two days on, retiring from the sport, she wrote: \\\"Mother, wrestling won, I lost.\", \"from\": 4673, \"to\": 4753, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 4700, \"to\": 4709}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Forgive me that I broke your dream, but I do not have courage and energy anymore.\", \"from\": 4754, \"to\": 4835, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your dream\", \"from\": 4778, \"to\": 4788}, {\"ngram\": \"courage\", \"from\": 4808, \"to\": 4815}, {\"ngram\": \"energy\", \"from\": 4820, \"to\": 4826}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Goodbye wrestling 2001-2024, I will always be indebted to your support.\", \"from\": 4837, \"to\": 4909, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your support\", \"from\": 4896, \"to\": 4908}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Forgive me.\\\"\", \"from\": 4910, \"to\": 4922, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Join thought-provoking conversations, follow other Independent readers and see their replies Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in\", \"from\": 4924, \"to\": 5154, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4975, \"end\": 4986, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.968975263298537e-20, \"text\": \"Independent\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"thought-provoking conversations\", \"from\": 4929, \"to\": 4960}, {\"ngram\": \"their replies\", \"from\": 5003, \"to\": 5016}, {\"ngram\": \"the page\", \"from\": 5032, \"to\": 5040}, {\"ngram\": \"another page\", \"from\": 5056, \"to\": 5068}, {\"ngram\": \"the site\", \"from\": 5072, \"to\": 5080}, {\"ngram\": \"inPlease\", \"from\": 5108, \"to\": 5116}, {\"ngram\": \"your browser\", \"from\": 5125, \"to\": 5137}]}]}"